老鹰乐队成员唐·亨利提起诉讼，要求归还他手写的《加州旅馆》音符和歌词https://www.nme.com/news/music/eagles-don-henley-sues-for-the-return-of-his-handwriting-hotel-california-notes-and-lyrics-3770661?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=老鹰唐亨利起诉归还他手写的加州酒店笔记和歌词Alex RigottiSun, 30 Jun 2024 17:51:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3770661 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="唐·亨利（Don Henley）（岩村由纪/法新社摄影）（岩村由纪/法新社摄影，盖蒂图片社）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在此之前的一起刑事案件在三月份突然被撤销，当时法官得出亨利“操纵”检方的结论</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eagles-don-henley-sues-for-the-return-of-his-handwritten-hotel-california-notes-and-lyrics-3770661">老鹰乐队成员唐·亨利 (Don Henley) 起诉要求归还他手写的《加州旅馆》音符和歌词，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="唐·亨利（Don Henley）（岩村由纪/法新社摄影）（岩村由纪/法新社摄影，盖蒂图片社）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Don-Henley-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eagles">老鹰乐队</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/don-henley">唐·亨利</a>已提起诉讼，要求归还他在《加州旅馆》专辑中的手写音符和歌词。</p><p>据<a href="https://apnews.com/article/hotel-california-lyrics-trial-eagles-don-henley-9f85617671ecb6bd62985455e4082731" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>美联社报道</em></a>，亨利于周五（6 月 27 日）向纽约联邦法院提起民事诉讼。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/judge-says-don-henley-manipulated-prosecutors-and-dismisses-case-over-eagles-hotel-california-lyrics-3597981">在此之前，三月份曾发生一起针对三名收藏品专家的案件</a>，他们被指控试图出售这些纸币。然而，法官在得出唐·亨利通过隐瞒证据“操纵”检察官的结论后中途撤销了此案：“现在很明显，[亨利和老鹰队的长期经理欧文·阿佐夫]和他们的律师[……]利用特权来混淆和隐藏他们认为歌词被盗的信息会损害他们的地位。</p><p> “尽管为时已晚，我还是赞扬检方拒绝让自己或法院为了任何人的个人利益而受到进一步操纵。地方检察官布拉格和这里的检察官团队在吃着一块不起眼的馅饼的同时，在撤销指控方面表现出了最高水平的正直。我很佩服。”此后亨利坚称文件被盗。</p><p>现在，亨利已对善本经销商格伦·霍洛维茨、前摇滚名人堂馆长克雷格·因西亚迪和摇滚纪念品销售商爱德华·科辛斯基提起诉讼。老鹰乐队联合创始人丹尼尔·彼得罗切利 (Daniel Petrocelli) 在亨利的律师丹尼尔·彼得罗切利 (Daniel Petrocelli) 的一份声明中声称，“这 100 页的个人歌词属于亨利先生及其家人，他从未授权被告或任何其他人以盈利为目的兜售这些歌词。” </p><figure id="attachment_3150176" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3150176" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3150176" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/donhenley-theeagles-2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="老鹰队的唐·亨利" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/donhenley-theeagles-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/donhenley-theeagles-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/donhenley-theeagles-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/donhenley-theeagles-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/donhenley-theeagles-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/donhenley-theeagles-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3150176" class="wp-caption-text">老鹰乐队 (The Eagles) 的唐·亨利 (Don Henley) 于 2019 年进行现场表演。图片来源：Simone Joyner/Getty Images </figcaption></figure><div data-module="" data-class="sovrn-story-feed" data-delayadinsertion="" data-ad-position="3"><p>科辛斯基和因西亚迪的律师称该诉讼“毫无根据”，并表示亨利的最初审判因误导检方而被撤销。科辛基的律师在一份声明中表示，“唐·亨利迫切希望改写历史”，并补充道：“我们期待对此案提起诉讼，并对亨利提起诉讼，追究他反复撒谎和滥用司法系统的责任。”</p><p>与此同时，因西亚迪的律师斯泰西·里奇曼在另一份声明中声称，该诉讼是企图“欺凌”和“延续虚假叙述”。霍洛维茨的律师没有回复寻求置评的电子邮件。 </p></div><div class="SovrnAd Advertisement sovrn-story-feed proper-dynamic-insertion" data-module="" data-class="sovrn-story-feed" data-delayadinsertion="" data-ad-position="3">老鹰队最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eagles-extend-their-sphere-residency-with-eight-more-shows-3769334">延长了他们的 Sphere 驻场演出，增加了八场演出</a>。 </div><div data-module="" data-class="sovrn-story-feed" data-delayadinsertion="" data-ad-position="3"></div><div data-module="" data-class="sovrn-story-feed" data-delayadinsertion="" data-ad-position="3"><p>本月早些时候，乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eagles-announce-las-vegas-sphere-residency-3765557">确认了他们即将到来的 Sphere 驻场演出，</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eagles-rumoured-for-las-vegas-residency-3604202">此前三月份就有传言称</a>他们是下一个在内华达州大型音乐厅亮相的音乐家。</p><p>现在，老鹰队宣布了新一轮的比赛日期，他们将在这个巨大的地球仪上一直比赛到今年 12 月 14 日。查看以下所有日期并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/eagles-tickets/artist/734977?irgwc=1&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272&amp;clickid=WelXSo2cHxyKR7zUPb3vE3Q-UkC0HG0BnRItQA0">在此处</a>获取所有剩余门票：</p><h3><strong>老鹰队 2024 年 Sphere 驻场演出是：</strong></h3><p><strong>九月</strong><br /><strong>星期五, 20</strong><br /><strong>星期六, 21</strong><br /><strong>星期五, 27</strong